{"tid":2312516,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「元秋」蔣麗芸家族骨肉相殘 深圳直擊震雄地皮 揭蔣家姊弟火併內幕","createTime":"2020-12-05T04:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T04:35:35.000Z","uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccc297b7c485ea224c705f7c671aedcf56232e9","tid":2312516,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:34:12.000Z","msg":"「元秋」蔣麗芸家族骨肉相殘 深圳直擊震雄地皮 揭蔣家姊弟火併內幕<br />\n<br />\n外號「元秋」的立法會議員蔣麗芸，在政界言論出位，不時淪為被恥笑對像，不過她老父蔣震是一代香港工業家，創辦震雄集團（57），在工業界地位舉足輕重。蔣震家族向來團結，2011年四女蔣麗莉捲入官司，一家人齊心高調現身庭外以示支持。但此情不再，自從去年蔣震退休，由六女蔣麗苑接任主席，她就充當「勇武派」全面改革公司，由工業轉型搞地產，更引入「外援」，但「建制派」、即任副主席的蔣震孻仔蔣志堅處處反對，令蔣麗苑部署踢走細佬，本刊到深圳直擊有關地皮，揭開兩姊弟爭權始未。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/U52E1rJobbb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FU52E1rJobbb&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wz44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=2683e15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/U52E1rJobbb</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAhpy6RFhns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhAhpy6RFhns&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wz44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=98d31aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAhpy6RFhns</a>"},{"pid":"22bd425fefc8fb85599bc98f4be76f6fb6c6878a","tid":2312516,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"樓主考車加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}